    "name": "Heaven Crawler",
    "steam_appid": 3036360,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Heaven Crawler</strong> is a cute, but very challenging roguelite dungeon crawler. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/aee48a24d20ce6ef0eef161330d48a37.poster.avif?t=1759770792\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/aee48a24d20ce6ef0eef161330d48a37.webm?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/aee48a24d20ce6ef0eef161330d48a37.mp4?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Epic maquete visual style, in an isometric, vibes-filled, Heavenly Diorama!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Indulge yourself with a fresh look within the genre, designed to enhance a journey of colossal proportions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/f17a5a256faf0412b41b53f8fc9ba9db.poster.avif?t=1759770792\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/f17a5a256faf0412b41b53f8fc9ba9db.webm?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/f17a5a256faf0412b41b53f8fc9ba9db.mp4?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make your way through rooms full of automatas to ascend the tower</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The tower, riddled with mystery and secrets, is layered in Biomes. Each with unique rooms, traps, challenges and enemies to defeat. Gain souls, level up, get better equipment and improve each run! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/4eb9f656adeaabb0c5bf1282718d73eb.poster.avif?t=1759770792\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/4eb9f656adeaabb0c5bf1282718d73eb.webm?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/4eb9f656adeaabb0c5bf1282718d73eb.mp4?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mix-and-match Gear, Magic, Skills and Relics to build your own playstyle!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no classes in the game, instead each item unlocks diferent stats and abilities for you to choose and make your own! They can also be upgraded!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/427ec558866d0998baab9385f237310b.poster.avif?t=1759770792\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/427ec558866d0998baab9385f237310b.webm?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/427ec558866d0998baab9385f237310b.mp4?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be wary and use the Elements to your favor in order to master each Zone!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are over 7 fully reactive elements, like electricty, fire, ice and corrosion. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/2fbd0c205b9e91e68f3f0fae2eda2e03.poster.avif?t=1759770792\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/2fbd0c205b9e91e68f3f0fae2eda2e03.webm?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/2fbd0c205b9e91e68f3f0fae2eda2e03.mp4?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Physics-based combat and strategy!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use physics to your favor and throw, push, break and evade fully breakable props and enemies, but be wary of falling!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/8ef89da2cdacbfca758b5d00ab26cc3b.poster.avif?t=1759770792\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/8ef89da2cdacbfca758b5d00ab26cc3b.webm?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/8ef89da2cdacbfca758b5d00ab26cc3b.mp4?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Buy, Upgrade &amp; Expand your Equipment</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can unlock NPC's by setting them free, rescuing or defeating them on your way up. They will aid you in your journey with their unique systems, shops and more!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/67b53afc5ba8d53312f63ae1ecda7b57.poster.avif?t=1759770792\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/67b53afc5ba8d53312f63ae1ecda7b57.webm?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/67b53afc5ba8d53312f63ae1ecda7b57.mp4?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Interact with the world to learn about The Womb and the world left behind!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with NPC robots that are also making their way through the tower, seek their help and learn from their mistakes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/7d65e13774ab5a8419e79733992d3905.poster.avif?t=1759770792\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/7d65e13774ab5a8419e79733992d3905.webm?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/7d65e13774ab5a8419e79733992d3905.mp4?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >At the end of each Biome a Colossal Boss awaits your mastery!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is a Big Boss at the end of each Zone, as well as other secrets and mini Bossess to test your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/8e3db7b541fbf14a8690b97a23e9271e.poster.avif?t=1759770792\" width=598 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/8e3db7b541fbf14a8690b97a23e9271e.webm?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/8e3db7b541fbf14a8690b97a23e9271e.mp4?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Each defeat is an opportunity to learn and grow!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everytime you die, you go back to lobby with some of your souls and losing all your Satchel, but gain Research and Profficency on the equipment you used, as well as new adquired information, improving your chances for your next run. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/90bea58d50f0b7771761789a8240faae.poster.avif?t=1759770792\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/90bea58d50f0b7771761789a8240faae.webm?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/90bea58d50f0b7771761789a8240faae.mp4?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Full Game will Feature:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 Elemental Modifiers </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 8 Zones with unique Hazards </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 10+ Multi-phase Bosses </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ NPC’s to interact with </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 20+ Traps with Elemental Modifiers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40+ Enemies with unique Behaviour </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ Gear and Items to Mix-n-Match </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Endless Rooms &amp; Possibilities</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Beautiful Orchestral Soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WISHLIST NOW</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/3ca3b860614ac3056c72d177adbc3d00.poster.avif?t=1759770792\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/3ca3b860614ac3056c72d177adbc3d00.webm?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036360/extras/3ca3b860614ac3056c72d177adbc3d00.mp4?t=1759770792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
